A simple Arduino-based MIDI footswitch.
The following version is use to change Programs and Banks on the NordStage2 keyboard.
(it is possible to adapt it for other music instrument)

Features PREVIOUS, NEXT and MODE buttons.

COMPONENTS:
- Arduino Uno
- TM1637 4-DIGIT LED DISPLAY
- 3x momentary buttons
- 220ohm Resistor
- DIN5 MIDI Connector


NOTE: this is just an early prototype. A more complex project involving WiFi and OSC is on the way.

video demo: https://youtu.be/nQlQ2tHXT1o
